user_profile.description:
At CoComelon, our primary goal has always been to engage families with entertaining and educational content that makes universally-relatable preschool moments fun. 
Our beautiful 3D animation and toe-tapping songs create a world that centers on the everyday experiences of young children. 
In addition to helping preschoolers learn letters, numbers, animal sounds, colors, and more, 
the videos impart prosocial life lessons, providing parents with an opportunity to teach and play with their children as they watch together.

CoComelon. Where kids can be happy and smart!

Website ► https://cocomelon.com/ 
Facebook ►https://www.facebook.com/CoComelonKids 
Instagram ►https://www.instagram.com/cocomelon_official/ 
TikTok ► https://www.tiktok.com/@cocomelon
US Shop ► https://shop.moonbug.com/collections/cocomelon

recent_posts.text:
🐝SUBSCRIBE for new Lellobee cartoons and songs every week!

It’s a stormy day on Lellobee City Farm. Thunder is rumbling and lightning is flashing. Ella is a bit frightened by it all but Grandma Mei shows her that there is nothing to be scared of. They both watch the animals having fun outside and when the storm has passed Ella joins them to jump in puddles!

🐝Lellobee City Farm is a new kids cartoon show from the creators of CoComelon.

There’s a thunderstorm
It isn’t very warm
It’s really wet outside
Oh my - let’s sit by the window
And we will hear the sounds
Of raindrops pouring down
But please don’t be afraid
It’s okay
On this thunderstormy day

Do you hear that sound - crack crack crack 
That’s a lightning bolt
And there’s the big low rumble of the thunder! 

Look at all the clouds
They’re dark but anyhow
There’s nothing we should fear
We’re all here
On this thunderstormy day

Storms are cool

The rain has gone away
So let’s go out and play
Get on your rubber boots
Look at that!
The clouds are clearing up now!
What a special day 
In a stormy way
We weren’t afraid you see
You and me
On Lellobee!
A stormy day
On Lellobee!
